# MCP LanceDB Development Guide

## 🛠️ **Development Workflow** 

### **Setup (Enterprise-Grade)**
```bash
# Environment setup
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # or `.venv\Scripts\activate` on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Quick validation (integration tests most critical)
pytest tests/integration/ -q

# Performance verification
python -c "from mcp_lancedb import list_tables, optimize_table; list_tables(); print('✅ LanceDB best practices active')"
